\c 6
\s Kusazvifunga kwaPauro pakuparidza kwake
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvatinobatawo pamwechete, tinokumbira zvikuruwo kuti murege kugamuchira nyasha dzaMwari pasina.
\v 2 Nokuti unoti: Nenguva yakafanira ndakakunzwa, uye napazuva roruponeso ndakakubatsira. Tarirai, zvino nguva yakafanira; tarirai zvino zuva rokuponeswa.
\v 3 Hatigumbusi nechinhu, kuti kushumira kurege kuzvidzwa;
\v 4 asi pazvose tinozviratidza savashumiri vaMwari, pakutsungirira kukuru, pakutambudzika, pakushaiwa, pakumanikidzwa,
\v 5 pakurohwa, pakusungwa, pabongozozo, pamabasa, pakusavata, pakutsanya;
\v 6 pautsvene paruzivo, pamoyo murefu, paunyoro, paMweya Mutsvene, parudo rusinganyengeri;
\v 7 pashoko rechokwadi, pasimba raMwari, nezvombo zvokururama, kurudyi nokuruboswe,
\v 8 nokukudzwa, nokusakudzwa, neguhu rakaipa, neguhu rakanaka; savanyengeri, asi \add tiri\add* vechokwadi;
\v 9 savasingazikamwi, asi tichizikamwa zvikuru; savanofa, asi, tarirai, tiri, vapenyu; savanorohwa, asi tisingaurawi;
\v 10 savanoshungurudzwa, asi tichigara tichifara; savarombo, asi tichifumisa vazhinji; savasine chinhu, asi tinazvo zvose hedu.
\s Vatsvene ngavaparadzane nezvakaipa zvose
\p
\v 11 Haiwa imwi, vaKorinde, muromo wedu wakashama kwamuri, moyo wedu wakuriswa.
\v 12 Hamumanikidzwi matiri, asi munomanikidzwa mumoyo menyu.
\v 13 Zvino, mundidzosere saizvozvo ndinotaura sokunavana \add vangu\add*, imivo mukuriswe.
\v 14 Musasungwa zvisina kufanira pajoko pamwe chete navasingatendi; nokuti kururama kungava nokudyidzana kweiko nokusarurama? Chiedza chingabatana seiko nerima?
\v 15 Kristu unokunzwana kweiko naBeriari? Unotenda ungava nomugove weiko nousingatendi?
\v 16 Tembere yaMwari ingatenderana chiiko nezvifananidzo? Nokuti imwi muri tembere yaMwari mupenyu; Mwari sezvaakareva \add achiti\add*: Ndichagara mukati mavo, nokufamba mavari; ndichava Mwari wavo, uye ivo vachava vanhu vangu.
\v 17 Naizvozvo budai pakati pavo, muraurwe, ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe, uye musabata chine tsvina; zvino ini ndichakugamuchirai,
\v 18 Uye ndichava Baba venyu, nemwi muchava vanakomana navanasikana vangu. Ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe unesimba rose.
